6. Usage

These scripts are intended to enable Windows-based Winlink applications to run on Linux and macOS via Wine. Supported applications include those available at downloads.winlink.org
.

7. Unsupported Software

The following software has not been tested and is not currently supported by these scripts:

SCS USB Driver 2.08.24 WHQL Certified
(downloads.winlink.org - /Sysop Programs/SCS USB Driver 2.08.24 WHQL Certified/)

Note: USB kernel drivers such as the above are not compatible with Wine and require a native Windows environment or a dedicated Windows virtual machine.
